Ri referred to a joint statement issued by Kim Jong Un and Donald Trump at the first ever summit held between a U.S. President and a North Korean leader in Singapore on June 12, where Kim undertook to work towards \"the denuclearization of the Korean peninsula\" while Trump offered security guarantees to North Korea.
